Befriend Animal or Plant

This spell, in combination with a druid's animal empathy,
may allow him to befriend a wild animal.  If successfully
befriended, the animal will serve the druid willingly to
the best of its ability, even fighting to the death if
the druid requests it.  Plant-like monsters may also be
charmed with this spell, but not humanoids or other
creatures.

Command: befriend <target>
Base Cost: 125 SP
Base Recovery: slow
Base Effect: follower
Base Duration: permanent (until logoff)
Guild Level: 13
